---------
about
---------

cocktail is an actionscript full stack framework built to deploy fast rich
internet applications with a robust & high level interactive and data driven
development style.



---------
fast tips
---------

1. add the "src" and "demo/src" folders to classpath.

2. add all "swc" inside "vendors" to classpath.

3. make the "demo/src/Codeine.as" (document class) export it's swf named
"core.swf" inside "demo/www/cocktail/swf/".

4. create a symbolic link from "demo/www" folder into your webserver root
folder, so you can acces it @ localhost.

5. after compile, launch "http://localhost/symbolic_link_name" to see the demo
working.
